channel.title: Rooney-474 | Coming Soon | Not a remake!
channel.description:
[center]Hello & welcome to the official Rooney-474 Project thread! This project will not be a remake but it will not be like any other 474 you've played. This is a late development thread.
[b]Features[/b] Pest Control Fight Caves minigames full 63 waves Clipped following (Npc's & Players) Many Bosses to battle Holiday items will be given out exactly like runescape Firemaking Woodcutting Herblore And many more skills Sailing! Pyramid Plunder cluescrolls Working agility shortcuts Moving textures And much much more!
Media [img]http://puu.sh/1hoDS[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/1hoGz[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/1hoPN[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/1hoWW[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/1hBOV[/img] If someone could possibly make me a support banner and a forums banner that would be awesome! Will post more pictures very soon![/center]
